# Context-Aware Adaptive Memory Management — Solution Walkthrough

## Problem Statement Summary
Build an intelligent memory manager for on-device AI that dynamically allocates resources based on user context, predicts next apps for pre-loading, and implements adaptive caching to beat standard LRU.

---

## Solution Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["User Activity Log<br/>(App switches, timestamps)"] --> B["Ensemble Predictor"]
    B --> C["LSTM + Attention<br/>(30% weight)"]
    B --> D["Per-User Markov Chain<br/>(70% weight)"]
    C --> E["P(next_app) distribution"]
    D --> E
    E --> F["Adaptive Memory Manager"]
    F --> G["Prediction-Weighted Eviction"]
    F --> H["Proactive Pre-Loading"]
    F --> I["Anti-Thrashing Guard"]
    F --> J["KV Cache Compression"]
    G --> K["KPI Benchmarks"]
    H --> K
    I --> K
    J --> K
```

